# PLAYER::GET_CAUSE_OF_MOST_RECENT_FORCE_CLEANUP

## Summary
Returns the flag that caused force cleanup to trigger. It only makes sense to call this after HAS_FORCE_CLEANUP_OCCURRED has returned TRUE

## Returns
* **INT**
